comments: Green (GSW) establishes himself in a wide picking stance and extends his knee into Matthews? (LAL) path.
Green (GSW) legally firms up in Caruso's (LAL) path.
Davis (LAL) makes contact with Curry's (GSW) arm prior to his gather.
Caldwell-Pope (LAL) establishes himself in a legal picking position in Wiggins' (GSW) path.
As Caldwell-Pope (LAL) releases from the pick, he makes marginal contact with Wiggins' (GSW) back.
Caldwell-Pope (LAL) gathers the ball with his right foot planted and legally takes two steps.  He then maintains his pivot foot before making the pass.
Curry (GSW) legally contests James' (LAL) jump shot attempt.
Davis (LAL) remains vertical and absorbs the contact as Curry (GSW) jumps into Davis on the pass.
Davis (LAL) legally contests Poole's (GSW) jump shot attempt.
Poole (GSW) makes marginal contact with Caldwell-Pope's (LAL) arm as they move off ball.
Curry (GSW) legally contests Matthews' (LAL) jump shot attempt.
Caldwell-Pope (LAL) briefly engages then disengages with Curry (GSW) during the inbounds play.
Davis (LAL) and Curry (GSW) engage in marginal contact as Curry attempts to receive the throw-in.
